{"word":"H3591 - כִּידֹון - kîydôwn - kee-dohn' - Lance","slug":"H3591","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כִּידֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kîydôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kee-dohn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Lance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05D9;&#x05D3;&#x05D5;&#x05DF; - k&#x0131;&#x0302;ydo&#x0302;n</b> - <i>kee-dohn'</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/H3589\">H3589</a>; properly something to <i>strike</i> with, that is, a <i>dart</i> (perhaps smaller than <a href=\"#/H2595\">H2595</a>): - lance, shield, spear, target."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3592\">H3592</a>, <a href=\"#/H3594\">H3594</a>, <a href=\"#/H3597\">H3597</a>, <a href=\"#/H3599\">H3599</a>"}]}